<div id="recommendedReads" class="recommended-reads d-none d-sm-none d-md-none d-lg-block d-xl-block">
<h2 class="recommended-reads__intro-text">
<em>Granta</em> 167: Extraction Online </h2>
<a href="https://granta.com/you-are-the-product-hildyard/">
<div class="recommended-reads__item">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-2 col-md-4 recommended-reads__item-image_outer_container">
<div class="recommended-reads__item__image-container">
<img width="100" height="100" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20100%20100'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt data-lazy-src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/extraction-feature-1-100x100.jpg" /><noscript><img width="100" height="100" src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/extraction-feature-1-100x100.jpg" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt="" /></noscript> </div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-10 col-md-8">
<h3 class="recommended-reads__item__title">
You Are the Product </h3>
<p class="recommended-reads__item__excerpt">
‘The anglophone world, we have to infer, has run out of words for its own feelings.’ <br> <br>
Daisy Hildyard on the wisdom of scarecrows. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</a>
<a href="https://granta.com/you-are-the-product-fishman/">
<div class="recommended-reads__item">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-2 col-md-4 recommended-reads__item-image_outer_container">
<div class="recommended-reads__item__image-container">
<img width="100" height="100" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20100%20100'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt data-lazy-src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/extraction-feature-2-100x100.jpg" /><noscript><img width="100" height="100" src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/extraction-feature-2-100x100.jpg" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt="" /></noscript> </div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-10 col-md-8">
<h3 class="recommended-reads__item__title">
You Are the Product </h3>
<p class="recommended-reads__item__excerpt">
‘What is the read receipt for?’ <br> <br>
Lillian Fishman on texting, power and the ethics of leaving a friend on read. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</a>
<a href="https://granta.com/you-are-the-product-mclaughlin/">
<div class="recommended-reads__item">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-2 col-md-4 recommended-reads__item-image_outer_container">
<div class="recommended-reads__item__image-container">
<img width="100" height="100" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20100%20100'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt data-lazy-src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/extraction-feature-3-100x100.jpg" /><noscript><img width="100" height="100" src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/extraction-feature-3-100x100.jpg" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt="" /></noscript> </div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-10 col-md-8">
<h3 class="recommended-reads__item__title">
You Are the Product </h3>
<p class="recommended-reads__item__excerpt">
‘Like pretty much everyone who uses the internet, I have seen many terrible things that I did not search for and that I cannot unsee.’ <br> <br>
Rosanna McLaughlin on what the internet thinks she wants. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</a>
<a href="https://granta.com/you-are-the-product-dalla-rosa/">
<div class="recommended-reads__item">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-2 col-md-4 recommended-reads__item-image_outer_container">
<div class="recommended-reads__item__image-container">
<img width="100" height="100" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20100%20100'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt data-lazy-src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/extraction-feature-4-100x100.jpg" /><noscript><img width="100" height="100" src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/extraction-feature-4-100x100.jpg" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt="" /></noscript> </div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-10 col-md-8">
<h3 class="recommended-reads__item__title">
You Are the Product </h3>
<p class="recommended-reads__item__excerpt">
‘I have a pathological addiction to the internet, which I indulge with the excuse of making art. It rarely translates to anything good and mostly leaves me overstimulated and afraid.’ <br><br>
Paul Dalla Rosa on excess and the internet. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</a>
<a href="https://granta.com/two-poems-sylvia-legris/">
<div class="recommended-reads__item">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-2 col-md-4 recommended-reads__item-image_outer_container">
<div class="recommended-reads__item__image-container">
<img width="100" height="100" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20100%20100'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt data-lazy-src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/legris-feature-image-100x100.jpg" /><noscript><img width="100" height="100" src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/legris-feature-image-100x100.jpg" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt="" /></noscript> </div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-10 col-md-8">
<h3 class="recommended-reads__item__title">
Two Poems </h3>
<p class="recommended-reads__item__excerpt">
‘rumors of bees on speedwell, / no oxidative stress just / effortless pollination’ <br> <br>
Two poems by Sylvia Legris. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</a>
</div>

